50|$|The grey rhebok is a {{medium-sized}} antelope weighing 19 - 30 kg {{with a long}} neck, narrow ears, and <b>straight,</b> sharp <b>horns</b> in the male. The horns are ringed at the base and are around 15 - 25 cm long. Only the males carry the <b>straight</b> <b>horns.</b> The coat is short and dense and coloured in various shades of grey.|$|R
